sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as elevator.js
    participant A as scan-algorithm.js

    U->>UI: Enter requests, start, direction
    U->>UI: Click Visualize
    UI->>A: solve(requests, start, dir, maxFloor)
    A-->>UI: {order, distances, totalDistance, steps}
    UI->>UI: Render elevator shaft
    UI->>UI: Initialize step index = -1

    loop Playback (Play/Step)
        U->>UI: Step/Play
        UI->>UI: Advance stepIdx
        UI->>UI: Animate car to step.position
        UI->>UI: Update queue badges
        UI->>UI: Update distance counter
        UI->>UI: Update info panel
    end

    UI->>UI: Show final stats
